high_descs: Turn left, go to end of counter on left.  Turn left to face counter with toaster on it.
Pick up green sponge from counter in front of toaster.
Turn right, go to sink on right.  Turn left, go to counter.  Turn right, proceed to stove.
Place sponge in pan on back right burner.
Pick up pan with sponge from back right burner.
Turn around, proceed past counter.  Turn right, proceed to wall.  Turn left to face table.
Put pan with sponge on table below the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Take sponge from counter, place on pan on stove, pick both up, move to table.

high_descs: Go to the left to the counter where the toaster is.
Pick up the sponge that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, go to the sink, turn to the left, go to the counter, hang a right and go to the stove.
Put the sponge in the pan on the back right side of the stove.
Pick up the pan containing the sponge from the stove.
Go to the right, hang a right and go past the counter, hang a right and go to the dining table.
Put the pan on the table in front of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing a sponge on a table.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the sponge on the counter to the right.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Bring the sponge to the stove, behind you to the left.
Put the sponge in the pan on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the pan with sponge on the stove.
Turn around, bring the pan with sponge to the round table in the far corner on the right.
Put the pan with sponge on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with sponge on the round table.
